    // -------------------------------------------------------------------------
    //
    // 1. Ensure that the node has a maximum width after which truncation
    //    can occur.
    // 2. Fix for IE 8/9 if `word-wrap: break-word` is in effect on ancestor
    //    nodes.
    //
    // -------------------------------------------------------------------------

